  "keyFeatures": [
    "Dipole geomagnetic field model and plasma density parameterizations (Sheeley, Carpenter-Anderson, Ozhogin, Denton)",
    "Cold and warm plasma wave dispersion relations (Appleton-Hartree, Stix formalism)",
    "Refractive index calculations for whistler-mode, EMIC, O-mode, X-mode, and L/R-mode waves",
    "Gyro-averaged nonlinear equations of motion for electron-whistler and ion-EMIC interactions",
    "Landau damping computation along ray paths with multiple particle distribution function models",
    "Ray path utilities for reading, appending, and plotting ray-tracing output files",
    "Test-particle simulation capability usable standalone or as an importable Python library",
    "Jupyter Notebook environment with integrated example notebooks and literature reproductions"
  ],
